>>>>>>>>ENGLISH>>>>>>>>

The EAOC crew's monthly night at The Obs is back, featuring only the most mouth-watering sounds from across the audio galaxy

This month, we have special guest GUSTAV LE BON, who is known in his native Cyprus as a serious techno & house force, regularly spinning at what is arguably the island nation’s foremost underground sound nightclub - Klubd. Specialized in weaving a constant, flowing and powerful blend of rare techno and house, he’ll be bringing this refined and particular audio aesthetic straight to The Observatory’s dance floor

As always, EAOC residents and founding sound brothas

>>> HIBIYA LINE - NIC FORD - DAN LO will be on hand providing the support from start to sunrise [and maybe beyond]

Sound Power Party

////// EAOC nights are all about bringing an eclectic mix of rare, dance-focused sound to the people of Saigon - from afrobeat & funk to disco, house & techno ////// 

doors 10PM
FREE entrance before 11PM / 100K after

